
### Colección de Pruebas - StockFlow API

### Variables de entorno (modifica el puerto si es necesario)
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000/api
@adminToken = {{loginAdmin.response.body.data.token}}
@operatorToken = {{loginOperator.response.body.data.token}}


# 1. AUTENTICACIÓN

### 1.1 Registro exitoso (usuario nuevo)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@stockflow.com",
  "password": "123456"
}

### 1.2 Registro duplicado (debe devolver 409)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@stockflow.com",
  "password": "123456"
}

### 1.3 Login como ADMIN (guarda el token automáticamente)
# @name loginAdmin
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@stockflow.com",
  "password": "Admin1234"
}

### 1.4 Login como OPERATOR
# @name loginOperator
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "operator@stockflow.com",
  "password": "Oper1234"
}

### 1.5 Login con credenciales inválidas (401)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@stockflow.com",
  "password": "equivocada"
}


# 2. PRODUCTOS

### 2.1 Listar todos los productos (público)
GET {{baseUrl}}/products

### 2.2 Filtrar por categoría "Electrónica"
GET {{baseUrl}}/products?category=Electrónica

### 2.3 Obtener producto por ID (1)
GET {{baseUrl}}/products/1

### 2.4 Crear producto (ADMIN) – token automático
POST {{baseUrl}}/products
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "name": "Tablet Samsung",
  "sku": "TAB-001",
  "stock": 20,
  "minStock": 5,
  "price": 299.99,
  "categoryId": 2
}

### 2.5 Intentar crear sin token (401)
POST {{baseUrl}}/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Test",
  "sku": "TST-001",
  "stock": 10,
  "minStock": 2,
  "price": 99.99,
  "categoryId": 1
}

### 2.6 Intentar crear con OPERATOR (403)
POST {{baseUrl}}/products
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{operatorToken}}

{
  "name": "Test Operator",
  "sku": "TST-002",
  "stock": 10,
  "minStock": 2,
  "price": 99.99,
  "categoryId": 1
}

### 2.7 Actualizar producto (ADMIN)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/products/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "stock": 25
}

### 2.8 Eliminar un producto creado (ADMIN)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/products/6
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}


# 3. PEDIDOS (TRANSACCIONAL)

### 3.1 Crear pedido válido (descuenta stock)
POST {{baseUrl}}/orders
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "items": [
    {"productId": 1, "quantity": 2},
    {"productId": 2, "quantity": 1}
  ]
}

### 3.2 Verificar stock del producto 1
GET {{baseUrl}}/products/1

### 3.2b Verificar stock del producto 2
GET {{baseUrl}}/products/2

### 3.3 Intentar pedido con stock insuficiente (error 400)
POST {{baseUrl}}/orders
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "items": [
    {"productId": 3, "quantity": 100}
  ]
}

### 3.4 Obtener detalles de un pedido (id 1)
GET {{baseUrl}}/orders/1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 3.5 Cambiar estado a DISPATCHED (ADMIN)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/orders/1/status
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "status": "DISPATCHED"
}

### 3.6 Intentar cancelar un pedido ya despachado (409)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/orders/1/status
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "status": "CANCELLED"
}

### 3.7 Cancelar un pedido PENDING con reintegro de stock
### Primero crea un nuevo pedido pequeño (guardamos su ID manualmente)
POST {{baseUrl}}/orders
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "items": [
    {"productId": 4, "quantity": 1}
  ]
}

### Ahora cancela el pedido recién creado (suponiendo ID = 2)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/orders/2/status
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "status": "CANCELLED"
}

### Verifica que el stock del producto 4 se reintegró
GET {{baseUrl}}/products/4

### 3.8 Doble cancelación (409)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/orders/2/status
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "status": "CANCELLED"
}


# 4. REPORTES (SÓLO ADMIN)

### 4.1 Productos con bajo stock (debe aparecer "Teclado mecánico")
GET {{baseUrl}}/reports/low-stock
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 4.2 Intentar acceder sin token (401)
GET {{baseUrl}}/reports/low-stock

### 4.3 Intentar con OPERATOR (403)
GET {{baseUrl}}/reports/low-stock
Authorization: Bearer {{operatorToken}}



